result.name: Deluxe Daieiki Japanese Restaurant

reviews.text: They offered value-for-money buffet for Japanese food. Many choices to choose and the tastes were quite good. I have been there twice and they keep the same quality. Good for meeting friends, but not for romantic dinning. Book in advance is recommended.

This was the best dining experience I had in Hong Kong. All you can eat Japanese with unlimited beer 😁 The menu is like a phone book where you rip out the pages and mark off what food you would like. The sushi was amazing, I tried almost every kind, I wasn't a big fan of the raw prawns, I find it hard to accept the raw texture 🤣 the desserts were amazing too, I tried all of these too. Thankfully there was a lift down as I could barely walk after eating so much 😂
It was an incredible and dare I say life changing experience. The food was amazing, the sushi was even better than what I’ve had in Japan. 10/10 recommend.
Price is reasonable and food quality is not bad

Excellent All-U-Can-Eat Japanese! Fantastic value for money at HKD 188 for lunch. All the sashimi and sushi were super fresh! As good as the top Japanese restaurants. The beef was super tender, must try. Go during lunch time as there are lot less people which means when you order your food, you get it within few minutes! Unlimited beer, sake, soju also.

reviews.text: A clean, well organised mall with more stores than you can imagine. Well maintained and hygienic restrooms as frequently spaced and the proximity to the MTR is a big plus!

Huge variety! It's great for shopping and dining 👍 they also have a cinema, for entertainment, showing a variety of Western and Asian movies. Pop-up stalls and exhibitions are constantly visiting the mall giving shoppers something interesting to do while walking from shop to shop, or just to celebrate the current events (popular movies, holidays, brands etc.)

Nothing special different from other plaza
It’s crowded. Many mainland people surrounded. 
Although it’s so many restaurant, you need to queue for the restaurant was extremely long.
And the price is not reasonable.
Very disappointed. 
Not recommend.
a grand n morden mall with variaties of dinning places, great to visit...

Many restaurants & cafe, you can find any kind of food & style, this should be the biggest shopping mall at Yuen Long area at moment, very convenient and easy to access, just a min. walk linked with West Rail Yuen Long station.

result.name: Deluxe Daieiki

reviews.text: Love it for the speedy service. If you want to have a quiet meal, go somewhere else. I love their early bird price. The food is very fresh. Definitely will go back!
Space is tight, but the service is qite good. Food quality is pretty good for the price.

Second time eating in this Japanese AYCE restaurant. Another great experience. Staff were friendly and efficient. You order food through app on your mobile. Food came quickly. Assorted sashimi was very fresh and tasty. Sushi was top notch, especially ikura. Can't remember how many rounds did we order that. Tempura was nice. Deep fried chicken cartilage, sprinkled with salt and lemon juice. Delicious. A great variety of drinks to choose from. Surprised to see a little sweets corner! Oh mine, self restraint is needed. Highly recommend this place.

A good Japanese all-you-can-eat restaurant.
With so many choices to start from, Sashimi is fresh and nice while hot dishes also wonderful. Definitely highly recommended but remember to book in advance as full easily.
Very good quality sashimi! A wide wide range of dishes, all-you-can eat. Must book a couple days ahead. Very popular

result.name: 極尚大瀛喜(元朗分店)

reviews.text: 黑松露金菇最正😋😋😋
低食👍

作為一個sell高質的日式放題，
老實講質素只是還好。。

海鮮剌身的新鮮度一般，
Sushi即叫即造，紫菜同飯都剛剛好。

燒物都ok，食左雞軟骨，牛舌and燒蝦👍🏻
炸物的選擇不多，大同小異，
吉列比天婦羅🍤出色😂
有我愛吃的炸榴連🤫
仲有d粥，火鍋，拉麵冷麵等等我無試🙈

出面有多款飲品甜品湯品糖果😊
乜都有d。。一定滿足到小朋友！
甜品款式特別，竟然有檸檬撻😍
品質不錯👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻

今日食星期六5點早場$248+10% /位，
價錢好侍應好勤快主動！
明明食到7點但六點半都未到就好焦急，
不過我地都明既，出面好多人已經到晒等入場，
所以拿拿聲食完就走🤣

喜歡日式放題的年輕人，大多數雀躍，熱熱鬧鬧大吃一頓。
這間放題，有自選或規定時間，相差廿十元，這裏吸引了許多食客光臨，要預約訂位。
店內的座位不多，檯子細細張，入內點食物要快手，嘴巴也要快快咀嚼，因選好的食物，會不斷送上，單單一個刺身，己佔了半張檯，限時2小時要離座。
食物首選刺身，好有氣派，新鮮好味，炸物的榴槤波波，一口芝士，芝麻雞翼，不錯！
略嫌壽可小小件，好迷你！ 
蟲草花膠湯，濃縮好飲！
甜品有蛋撻和蛋糕，還有中式的糖水，啤酒，熱茶和日本酒任飲，
細細枝樽裝水也任你喝。

選擇多又好味
_
每次黎元朗探親友，經過yoho mall都見依間放題好多人等位 。今日探完婆婆後，媽咪話想食依間放題好耐。一於臨過年前帶佢食餐好慰勞下佢。餐廳啲座位都幾闊坐得幾舒服，而且食物飲品選擇多，值得推介。
-
熟食區都有幾種選擇
分別有啲春卷、小炒同葡撻仔，刺身未黎之前可以食一round醫一醫肚先。
-
刺身就點左三文魚、酒煮榮螺片、日本玉子、北海道帶子同埋北寄貝
全部都好新鮮，最愛肥美厚切的三文魚！雪白帶子亦好鮮甜。encore左幾round 。
-
壽司就點左蟹籽、火焰三文魚、左口魚、鰻魚、蟹子、辣味螺肉。
飯團細細的，不會擔心太快飽肚😆
蒲燒鰻魚肉厚質感彈牙
經火炙後的左右魚及三文魚，魚油溢出，魚香滿載。十二萬分的滿足感
-
鹽燒海蝦燒得好出色，十分鮮甜
鹽燒雞軟骨串，惹味之餘又好有咬口。
-
食飽之後就想食甜野架啦
點左燒菠蘿同燒日本蕃薯仔！蕃薯仔細細粒又勁香同甜！好正
個菠蘿好鮮好juicy 媽咪都好中意食。加左幾次單 大家都大滿足
-
甜品區就要係啲monchi,mousse蛋糕同雪糕
-
飲品都好多選擇 ：汽水、啤酒、解茶都有 有凍有唔凍 ；還有我覺得好貼心嘅係有熱櫃，食完凍冰冰既刺身壽司，想飲熱飲暖一暖呢。仲有咖啡機 鮮豆漿同鮮果汁揀呢
